column5: 2011 OFC TOURNAMENT - STARTS FEBRUARY 1 2011  Team selections will be made Sunday January 30 Subsequent team selections will be done in groups of 10  Check out the 2011 OFC Tournament page for details: http://www.ofncommunity.com/forums/index.php?showforum=54
Just so happens I'll be on the water that day, hopefully catching an entry or two
Anyone else? You have till Saturday evening to get in on the first wave. Git'er done!
